Package: ialctl
Version: 6.30.0-infinite-memory
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Diego Nardoni <diego@nardoni.com>
Description: IAL Infrastructure CLI v6.30.0 - Infinite Conversational Memory
 Revolutionary AWS Infrastructure deployment with infinite conversational memory:
 - Infinite Memory (never forgets conversations or context)
 - DynamoDB + S3 Glacier persistence (cost: $0.15/user/month)
 - Bedrock Embeddings for semantic search
 - Smart context retrieval across sessions
 - Amazon Q-like interactive experience
 - Automatic memory resource deployment via ialctl start
 .
 Memory Features in v6.30.0:
 - Persistent User ID (unique per machine/user)
 - Cross-session conversation continuity
 - Semantic search with Bedrock Titan Embeddings
 - Automatic summarization with Claude
 - Smart context injection for queries
 - Memory commands: /stats, /history, /forget
 - Local cache fallback (works offline)
 .
 Infrastructure Features (Preserved):
 - Interactive Mode: ialctl → continuous chat
 - Single Command: ialctl "command" → direct execution
 - Smart Routing: conversation vs infrastructure detection
 - GitHub as source of truth
 - YAML template generation with cost guardrails
 - Complete audit trail and governance
 - Foundation bootstrap (45 resources including memory)
 .
 Memory Architecture:
 - DynamoDB: Hot storage for recent conversations
 - S3 + Glacier: Cold storage for conversation archive
 - Bedrock: Embeddings and summarization
 - Local Cache: Offline capability
 .
 v6.30.0 provides infinite conversational memory with
 enterprise-grade persistence and intelligent context retrieval.
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-boto3
Homepage: https://github.com/Diego-Nardoni/ial-infrastructure
